Articles.Content:
Does anyone else get this error message when loading KSP 1.0.5?

[FONT=courier new]Load(Model): Squad/Parts/Misc/PotatoRoid/PotatoRoid[/FONT]
[FONT=courier new]The hull has more than 255 polygons. This is invalid.[/FONT]

Not sure if it's new to 1.0.5 or was always there. Guessing its harmless but would love to clean up some of the log spam.

Note I'm using Windows 64-bit, if it matters.

[I](And no, I'm not expecting support in response to this message, just sending out a feeler to gauge whether this is a common / known issue. Sorry if this was the wrong thread to put this in).[/I]
Don't worry about it, it's an expected message in 1.0.5.
